name: Beauty and the Beast
description:
One of the main and strongest theme in my works is rebel women characters. Such as witches, destructive goddess and female mythic characters.
I've been searching of them from the past and make adaptation to my drawings. This digital illustration is one of them, which wandering around the theme "beauty and the beast". 
To buy signed screen print version also contact me on twitter.
